<li aria-level="1">MOAR QUESTIONS AND TIPS!
<ul>
<li aria-level="1">01:03:44 Steve-<a href="https://mgg.fm/1010">1010</a>-Set Your Mac not to ask you for a sudo password
<ul>
<li aria-level="1">If you edit your /etc/sudoers file (with visudo), and find the line that reads:
<ul>
<li aria-level="1">%admin          ALL = (ALL) ALL</li>
<li aria-level="1">and change it to</li>
<li aria-level="1">%admin          ALL = (ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
